metadata.name: 360 Hardflip
metadata.description:
"Flipped Out Designs" is a collaborative art project by STVSH and 3DSK8.

STVSH is an electronic music producer and sound designer.

3DSK8 is an animator, best known for his work on Skater XL.

"360 Hardflip" is the second piece for our collaborative project. An animation and 3D model of 3DSK8 (Wray) performing a 360 Hardflip with sound design and music by STVSH.
